Attach to an existing tmux session.

Attach to an existing tmux session.

attach_session(name, prompt = NULL)

Arguments

name

Numeric or string indicating the name of the existing session.
prompt

String containing a regular expression.

Value

A tmuxr_session.

Examples

new_session()
#> tmuxr session 0: 1 windows (created Sun Sep  3 13:28:01 2017) [80x23]
s <- attach_session(0)
